會累死建制派。大家點解唔日日問吓民建聯啲區議員同立法會議員，『你撐唔撐警』、『覺唔覺得警察濫用暴力』呢？記住問是非題，一係yes，一係no，咪畀位佢遊花園呀。」<br />\n<br />\nBy 政界猛人揭林鄭底牌 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1442226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1442226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6313746b4320048bb8fe3ccb53f3545806e919c0","tid":1442360,"uid":169869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:59:15.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88767aaf497d49ddf539115c06d83f060fecb007","tid":1442360,"uid":295888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T02:59:35.000Z","msg":"721未解決！"},{"pid":"a146a689ea9da38908575d24e7f782aa9e2100b7","tid":1442360,"uid":2734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:00:17.000Z","msg":"你開完呢個po已經唔會講錯野啦"},{"pid":"7a56486db1701976e2eb49a579aa152cc264f868","tid":1442360,"uid":295888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:00:28.000Z","msg":"㩒錯再嚟！<br />\n<br />\n721未解決！"},{"pid":"9d8a1596ae5b74c7b54d900530a5a14bd7cf5a96","tid":1442360,"uid":227788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:02:36.000Z","msg":"問返<br />\n- 有冇臨時 徵召人 充當 警員<br />\n- 而家所有執勤嘅警務人員 係唔係全部都係 香港永久性居民"},{"pid":"0cbbbf002f5ae588f4ec0b4ba250c68212f51180","tid":1442360,"uid":59447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:10:38.000Z","msg":"對準721<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n毋忘5大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497a716057f08f2c781bee5231bc3ec29038eea9","tid":1442360,"uid":91259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T03:29:10.000Z","msg":"武警在香港執勤時發生人命傷亡如何處理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f834bb0e9f50ea4af7795c678a4ff0e233cae93b","tid":1442360,"uid":91259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,